{"tid":1325543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港示威者當選《時代》25大互聯網具影響力人物","createTime":"2019-07-17T02:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T02:17:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"19a03944eeb3f71538c9c5508bfe3722d7b7751b","tid":1325543,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:09:48.000Z","msg":"美國《時代》雜誌選出25名最具影響力的互聯網人物，香港示威者上榜。《時代》指出，在香港反《逃犯條例》修訂示威中，沒有「領袖和大台」帶領，全靠示威者透過網上平台組織行動。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》指出，示威者利用網上討論區「連登」和加密即時通訊軟件Telegram，組織反修例行動，包括遊行到多國駐港領事館請願及包圍警察總部等。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》引述一名Telegram頻道管理員，他形容行動過程是「直接民主（direct democracy）」。網民在連登提出不同行動方案引起關注，Telegram的投票、頻道廣播信息及聊天群組商討等功能，容讓示威者迅速動員或改變策略。組織行動以外，例如提醒下次遊行、法津支援、心理輔導和情緒支援等，也透過網上協調安排。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》提及，雖然部分升級行動，例如衝擊立法會出現反效果，但示威者透過集合眾人智慧的現有模式繼續抗爭。有份發起遊行的Ventus Lau向《時代》說：「我們相信人民的力量，因當我們發揮集體智慧時，我們作出的決定必定能夠較一群學生或領袖更好。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190717/s00001/1563324116386/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E3%80%8A%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%8B25%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%92%E8%81%AF%E7%B6%B2%E5%85%B7%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190717%2Fs00001%2F1563324116386%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E3%2580%258B25%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%2592%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2585%25B7%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=492062ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190717%2Fs00001%2F1563324116386%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E3%2580%258B25%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%2592%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2585%25B7%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9&h=307afdf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190717/s00001/1563324116386/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E3%80%8A%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%8B25%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%92%E8%81%AF%E7%B6%B2%E5%85%B7%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9</a>"},{"pid":"6f775b1bd7b92000238ab4c1e17a201f0c94ff27","tid":1325543,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2d8f72bb79a23eecb26f1fb629d98c740d5a6c","tid":1325543,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d98d970515fc57d05185bcef711a9e058bb76d4","tid":1325543,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"721 港島見 ! !<br />\n「全部同我將push改做721港島見」! ! !<br />\n唔準再推再Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663de073f3a2b30683c5cc44e0578ffe1203d328","tid":1325543,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112342b4fc2431eb3d6788e8c27eb502665d84df","tid":1325543,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:15:02.000Z","msg":"關連登撚事咩<br />\n又亂報新聞<br />\n明明係bk 香討勇武巴絲帶領成場運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d84bc429f8e9312842167aa9ed20059343d709c","tid":1325543,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"112342b4fc2431eb3d6788e8c27eb502665d84df","tid":1325543,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c